1. download the image writer from http://www.etcher.io/
$ chmod a+x Etcher-linux-x64.AppImage

2. download the prebuilt image from 
$ wget https://rcn-ee.com/rootfs/2016-06-09/microsd/bone-ubuntu-16.04-console-armhf-2016-06-09-2gb.img.xz
User: ubuntu pass: temppwd 

3. to connect through ssh 
ssh -X root@192.168.7.2

4. to shutdown the beaglebone
$ sudo shutdown -h now

5. to reboot the beaglebone
$ sudo reboot

http://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/158581/beaglebone-black-doesnt-connect-via-ethernet-on-laptop
